 956   std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> getSmallestAndWidestTypes();
 957 
 958   /// \return The desired interleave count.
 959   /// If interleave count has been specified by metadata it will be returned.
 960   /// Otherwise, the interleave count is computed and returned. VF and LoopCost
